textBeforeTable: Jefferson County follows the format "prefix-number". The prefix is determined by the municipality. The format is a three digit numeric municipal code, hyphen, four numeric digits( represents town and range), hyphen, four numeric digits (represents section & 1/4 1/4), hyphen, three numeric digit (represents an identifier). ^ Jefferson 186-xxxx.xxxx 186- TAYLOR, VILLAGE OF 042-xxxx.xxxx 042- SPRINGFIELD, TOWN OF 040-xxxx.xxxx 040- NORTHFIELD, TOWN OF 038-xxxx.xxxx 038- NORTH BEND, TOWN OF 036-xxxx.xxxx 036- MILLSTON, TOWN OF 152-xxxx.xxxx 152- MERRILLAN, VILLAGE OF 151-xxxx.xxxx 151- MELROSE, VILLAGE OF 034-xxxx.xxxx 034- MELROSE, TOWN OF 032-xxxx.xxxx 032- MANCHESTER, TOWN OF 030-xxxx.xxxx 030- KOMENSKY, TOWN OF 028-xxxx.xxxx 028- KNAPP, TOWN OF 026-xxxx.xxxx 026- IRVING, TOWN OF 136-xxxx.xxxx 136- HIXTON, VILLAGE OF 024-xxxx.xxxx 024- HIXTON, TOWN OF 022-xxxx.xxxx 022- GARFIELD, TOWN OF 020-xxxx.xxxx 020- GARDEN VALLEY, TOWN OF 018-xxxx.xxxx 018- FRANKLIN, TOWN OF 016-xxxx.xxxx 016- CURRAN, TOWN OF 014-xxxx.xxxx 014- CLEVELAND, TOWN OF 012-xxxx.xxxx 012- CITY POINT, TOWN OF 010-xxxx.xxxx 010- BROCKWAY, TOWN OF 206-xxxx.xxxx 206- BLACK RIVER FALLS, CITY OF 008-xxxx.xxxx 008- BEAR BLUFF, TOWN OF 006-xxxx.xxxx 006- ALMA, TOWN OF 101-xxxx.xxxx 101- ALMA CENTER, VILLAGE OF 004-xxxx.xxxx 004- ALBION, TOWN OF 002-xxxx.xxxx 002- ADAMS, TOWN
